description: The [PipeMon](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0501) installer has modified the Registry key HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Print\Environments\Windows x64\Print Processors to install [PipeMon](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0501) as a Print Processor.(Citation: ESET PipeMon May 2020)

external_references.description: Tartare, M. et al. (2020, May 21). No “Game over” for the Winnti Group. Retrieved August 24, 2020.
